{"id":589056,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/【立此存照】美籍宾客一律加收25！美方挑争端，我/","date":"2018-07-13T12:52:46Z","modified":"2018-07-13T12:52:46Z","title":"【立此存照】美籍宾客一律加收25%！美方挑争端，我方誓奉陪！","content":"<p>【编者按】中美贸易战擦枪走火，位于深圳的摩登克斯酒店 (Modern Classic Hotel)在7月6日发出公告，宣布酒店要对美国客人额外征收25%的客房费用。 流传网络的一份来自摩登克斯酒店的题为“郑重申明”（Solemnly Declare）的中英文双语海报写道——</p>\n<p>“摩登克斯国际酒店管理集团即将实施美籍宾客一律加收25%计划！美方挑争端，我方誓奉陪！”</p>\n<blockquote><p>相关阅读：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p class=\"title\">中央广播电台 | <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E5%B9%BF%E6%92%AD%E7%94%B5%E5%8F%B0-%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE%EF%BC%9A%E8%B4%B8%E6%98%93%E6%88%98%E5%BC%80%E6%89%93%EF%BC%8C%E6%B7%B1%E5%9C%B3%E9%85%92%E5%BA%97%E5%A2%9E/\">路透社：贸易战开打，深圳酒店增收美国客25%房费</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p class=\"title\">美国之音 | <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/07/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%B9%8B%E9%9F%B3-%E8%B4%B8%E6%98%93%E6%88%98%E6%B0%91%E7%B2%B9%E5%8C%96%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E9%A4%90%E5%8E%85%E7%BB%99%E7%BE%8E%E6%B8%B8%E5%AE%A2/\">贸易战民粹化 一中国餐厅给美游客“加税”</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_589057\" style=\"width: 235px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/摩登克斯酒店.png\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-589057\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/摩登克斯酒店-225x300.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/摩登克斯酒店-225x300.png 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/07/摩登克斯酒店.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\">深圳摩登克斯酒店”郑重声明“</p></div>\n","author":1056,"categories":[18270,18269,27949],"tags":[32327,14796]}